<L>__{interior hotel night}
<A>__{jack, in the corridor of a large modern hotel somewhere in the world. he is full of energy and playful excite ment. he's with a few of his colleagues, both men and women. they say good night to each other. everyone goes into his or her own room. jack's the last one, he goes into his room alone. his smile drops. for a moment he stands there just looking. he sits down on the bed: on the pillow is a little chocolate santa claus with a card that reads "merry christmas. the marriott hotels." jack contemplates it forlornly.}
